Description: System tray applet for on-demand rclone mount management
 RClone Mount Manager provides a lightweight system tray applet
 and GTK4-based GUI for managing rclone mounts on Linux.
 .
 Features:
  - System tray integration for quick mount control
  - Real-time mount status monitoring
  - One-click mount/unmount from tray menu
  - Modern GTK4-based configuration manager
  - Minimal resource usage
